cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.LG, cs.DC. 

The paper deals with an information update system, which involves communication and processing of data. Therefore, Information Theory (cs.IT) is the most likely category. The paper also discusses the generation of updates and their quality, which falls under Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI). The system involves decision-making and optimization, which can be categorized under Systems and Control (cs.SY). The paper also discusses policies and constraints, which can be categorized under Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC).
